Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives, Yahiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a good friend you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:24.00,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{typeset: 00:34 "Fire Extinguisher"}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Inori.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are Gai's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an insane, unfair world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouma, I have a question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close-fitting underwear or tights.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes called "spats" or "caleçon".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.92,0:00:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight letters long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:00:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got duped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "leggings"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, "leggings"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate leaving blank spaces in my puzzles, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'd like you to help fill in a few blanks for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've prepared a room you can think quietly in, though it's a bit small.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome to stay as long as it takes for you to solve my puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Shu was taken by GHQ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It surprised me too, so I confirmed it with the teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we still don't know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sounds like he's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Try doing a search on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought in Dr. Ouma's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I detained him on suspected ties to Undertaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have I offended you, Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not why I called. What's your impression?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guilty. There's no doubt he's tied to them somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are presents from Samukawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Tsutsugami Gai, the leader of Undertaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could a boy like you be doing in a place like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,talking to someone like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask Gai that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ouma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The food here isn't very good, I must say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't eaten those soft processed noodles since the school lunch line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think that over carefully before you say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, he's staying silent,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but considering that he calls their presumed leader by his first name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,despite displaying none of the ideological fixation typical of terrorists,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it appears he's no ordinary member.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, he's a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this, Major Segai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:05:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was sent to multiple news portals seven minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, Undertaker will raid GHQ's Isolation Facility Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resistance is futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will rescue our comrade without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, an advance notice of their crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, I just had an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Circumstances have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I'll go ahead and tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologies for these elaborate precautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're currently in a state of emergency,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're forced to tighten security on a certain prisoner underneath that tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll save the details for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, there's something I'd like you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our isolation ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This entire facility was originally built for the sake of this ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the reason Samukawa sold you out is here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is not an addict.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar was a Norma Gene dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was inside the Roppongi blockade that day to make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, he desperately needed to make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look down there, and you'll see why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that sleeping there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Yahiro's younger brother. His name is Samukawa Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:06:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it your first time seeing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what an Apocalyse Virus patient looks like when he reaches Stage IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among other things, this is a cutting-edge facility for providing relief
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to those who were infected in an unforeseen accident
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or developed symptoms because the vaccine didn't agree with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago, the Apocalypse Virus pandemic
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.69,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{typeset 07:33 "Roppongi Deaths Top 1000"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the violent riot that arose from it, "Lost Christmas,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,spread disorder throughout this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We at GHQ managed to successfully bring the outbreak under control
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the vaccine we later developed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the world successfully regained a measure of order at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I can't forgive Undertaker
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for trying to disturb the order we're desperately working to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouma, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would a smart boy like you trample on our goodwill?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodwill, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of goodwill was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you referring to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, people were killed right in front of me! By you people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people in that fort are unregistered citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They also refuse regular inoculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could call it a hotbed of contagion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that makes it okay to kill them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our soldiers were killed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have hometowns, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think they wanted to die on foreign soil?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Gai said we were doing that to save the people in the fort!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why is he trying to free a mass murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man behind the Sky Tree bombing, Kido Kenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Undertaker has declared that they will take him from us by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouma, I'll tell you a little secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beware of people who tell you to believe in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're with Tsutsugami Gai,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please press the blue button twice, and then the red one once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will come to mete out the appropriate punishment on him
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where they may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Yuzuriha Inori...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a famous musician on the web, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's being deceived by Tsutsugami Gai as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you refuse us, I'll be forced to ask for her help next.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blooming wildflower...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I beg you, please tell me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do people fight and hurt each other?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Funell... why do I feel cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would Shu know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out here. You've got a meeting with your lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother hired me to be your lawyer. The name's Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about a thing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai—{sasuga our brilliant MC}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get right down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! Beginning hack of the main system.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place never gives us much time, you see, so we have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you ready to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the cameras and mikes off you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an ordeal for you! You must've been so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everything's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave everything to me, and I'll get you out of here for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying I'm stupid, I know. My question is, why are {\i1}you{\i0} here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain person is being confined here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to break him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kido Kenji, the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ogumo and the others are about to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kido's in solitary confinement underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you leave here, meet up with him immediately and draw out his Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty seconds later—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just assume I'll obey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not one of your people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they say something to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it? Galty, the chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai. Why are you fighting? What's it for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Gai! You haven't told me a single—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention all personnel-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The system has gone down due to an attack from an outside hacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are currently rebooting from a backup array.{what would prevent it from being hacked again?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your turn, Gumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Engage the anti-air defenses! Get the Endlaves out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aya! Enemy units activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. I'm all set to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angle and direction, good. Can you do it, Ayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time. Decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to move, or come to a standstill again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming... {\i1}here{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I ordered you to stand by! Why are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai, I've located Inori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She broke into the facility solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's downloaded the coordinates of Shu's cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must intend to rescue him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But I'm in this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good. She's shut off her communicator.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the tower's defenses are super beefed up right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The interview's over! Get back to your cell pronto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! If you resi—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi, connect me with Shibungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye-aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to send Ayase in to assist your escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have an unexpected situation here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm changing our strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll secure Kido on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too reckless, Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase, you come in as planned. I need you to back up Shu and Inori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. Shibungi, I'm launching Steiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu, Inori, please just sit still!{but Inori wasn't even sitting!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai, Kido's started moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our chance. Send me his position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye-aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secured escapee. Currently checking his number. Request immediate—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to Inori?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've done something, otherwise she'd never disobey Gai's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole operation's screwed up thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to Gai, I swear I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, we have a message from the head of Isolation Facility Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We'll protect the facility on our own. Don't interfere."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. All right, I'm going out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, Sir, they said not to interfere...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to watch. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your big brother will protect you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep tight and don't worry, Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but go hide for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kido Kenji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! So his power is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You caught on, eh? Kido Kenji's Void has the power to manipulate gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to them. They just won't quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit... there are too many!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got no chance! Surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori... can I believe in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in the way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Kido, he's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Ayase, collect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't decide, then believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entrust me with everything. But {\i1}obey my orders{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{typeset "End Card Illustration: Abara Heiki"}
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.59,0:21:25.59,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}These days you love me no more
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.22,0:21:32.22,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}nor am I still treasured by you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.60,0:21:41.02,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Now I am all alone
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.82,0:21:48.91,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}What did you tell me when we parted?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.53,0:21:55.54,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}The words hung in midair and never reached me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.00,0:22:02.30,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}I know my dreams and wishes are illusory
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.88,0:22:08.93,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}and yet I cannot give up on them
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.97,0:22:18.94,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}You said, "Don't let go, hold onto my hand"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.48,0:22:25.94,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}and, "We will always be together"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.11,0:22:34.70,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Your hands as I held them were warm
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.83,0:22:43.00,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,2000)}and tender
